  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示用户和Service之间的交互。核心场景是用户请求Module 02，然后Service返回响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Service",
        "Module 02 request",
        "Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个参与者：User和Service。User发起请求，Service异步返回响应。我需要确认一下——Response是同步返回还是异步返回？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Service",
        "Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是异步返回，用虚线箭头表示。另外User的请求消息内容固定写成\"Module 02 request\"，Response就写\"Response\"就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Module 02 request",
        "Response",
        "虚线箭头"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来画。User指向Service的实线箭头标注\"Module 02 request\"，Service回User的虚线箭头标注\"Response\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Service",
        "Module 02 request",
        "Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，箭头方向好像反了？让我再看一下——不对，是消息文字需要调整。应该是\"Module 02 request\"而不是\"Module 2 request\"，要用带前导零的格式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Module 02 request"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，消息文字改为\"Module 02 request\"。现在User到Service是实线，Service到User是虚线，标注都正确了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Module 02 request",
        "User",
        "Service"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是这个效果。参与者别名也设置好，User显示为U，Service显示为S，这样图更简洁。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "S",
        "User",
        "Service"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认完成。U和S的别名已应用，交互流程清晰：用户请求Module 02，服务异步响应。图可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
